The paper discusses a system for reasoning on massive amounts of data, which suggests a focus on database systems (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also compares the performance of the proposed system with other logic programming systems (cs.LO) and commercial database systems (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper discusses the limitations of existing proposals and proposes a new system, which suggests a focus on software engineering (cs.SE).
